      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフのみなさん、撮影ありがとうございました！",
      "startTime": 2.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "CM撮影お疲れ様、渚。いい映像が撮れたと\nクライアントも満足そうだったぞ",
      "startTime": 11.2333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それに、衣装も似合っているな\nやはり渚にぴったりの仕事だったよ",
      "startTime": 16.7666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "私の好物が桃なので、それに合わせて\n桃の衣装にしてくれたらしくて……凄く嬉しいです！",
      "startTime": 23.0526076952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装を着たまま一日店長もやるんです\nまだまだ頑張りますよ！",
      "startTime": 30.8859409014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ。この前はありがとうございます\n新しいメニューの追加を頼んでもらっちゃって",
      "startTime": 37.0192728359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "問題ないよ。先方も、コラボメニューが増やせると\n二つ返事で了承してくれたしな",
      "startTime": 44.3333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "元々考えていたメニューと追加したメニュー\nどちらもお客さんが喜んでくれるといいんですけど……",
      "startTime": 50.4497262954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのために準備を頑張ってきたんだから\nきっと大丈夫だ",
      "startTime": 57.399999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね……！　一日店長、頑張ってきます！",
      "startTime": 59.399999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "いらっしゃいませー！\n月のテンペストの伊吹渚です！",
      "startTime": 67.3333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "美味しいフルーツジュースはいかがですかー？\n沢山の味を取り揃えておりまーす！",
      "startTime": 73.5666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "今日はなんと！　一日店長記念に\n私が考案したオリジナルメニューもあるんです！",
      "startTime": 80.0333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "私が大好きな桃をみんなに美味しく味わって\n欲しくて作った特別メニュー……",
      "startTime": 86.9333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "たっぷりの桃と優しい甘さがクセになる！\n『桃におぼれるフローズン』はいかがですか～？",
      "startTime": 93.3333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "他にも体が冷えてきた人にはフレッシュなフルーツを\nふんだんに入れたホットフルーツティー……",
      "startTime": 100.7999983151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "『寒さを吹き飛ばせ！　ホットホットフルーツ』\nもおすすめですよ～！",
      "startTime": 106.2333316485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "ご注文ありがとうございます！\n次の方どうぞー！",
      "startTime": 110.8999972979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "startTime": 113.6975490409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……さすがにちょっと疲れました……",
      "startTime": 115.6438435552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "渚、お疲れ様。大繁盛じゃないか\n特別メニューも好評だったみたいだな",
      "startTime": 124.0666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　みんなが喜んでくれて\n頑張って考えた甲斐がありました",
      "startTime": 129.5261916318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。スタッフさんから休憩中に飲んでくれって\nジュースをいただいたんです",
      "startTime": 135.8595168271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんもよかったら\nお一つどうですか？",
      "startTime": 139.2261834937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。これは……\n渚が考案したホットフルーツティーか",
      "startTime": 143.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "はい。追加で入れてもらったメニューです\n沢山売れたんですよ！",
      "startTime": 150.6669225531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりこの前、{user}さんと\n下見に行って良かったです",
      "startTime": 155.1002558865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "寒い時に冷たい飲み物を飲むと想像以上に\n体が冷えちゃうんだって気付けましたから",
      "startTime": 161.0002558865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前のことなのに、下見に行かなかったら\n見落としたままになっちゃってたかもしれません",
      "startTime": 167.7669225531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "実際に自分で経験してみるのって凄く\n大事なんだなって思いました！　ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 174.2669235704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに協力するのは当然のことだよ。それに渚なら\nきっとお客さんを喜ばせることが出来ると信じていた",
      "startTime": 183.2666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
